metadata.title: OshKosh B'Gosh Toddler and Little Boys Harbor Sandal
features: FUN CASUAL FOOTWEAR: Kids will be ready for all their warm-weather adventures in these classic sports sandals featuring wide straps
DURABLE CONSTRUCTION: Flat sandals with flexible outsole and lightweight upper provides comfort to the little feet
SLIP-ON SHOES: Kids can easily put-on or take-off these stylish shoes with the help of hook-and-loop strap and locker loops
EASY TO CLEAN: These shoes for children are machine washable and can be cleaned with a damp, warm cloth using mild liquid soap
PERFECT FOR ALL OCCASIONS: Kids will splash around all day in these stylish sandals which are great for walking, jogging, running, traveling, camping; Perfect for any indoor and outdoor adventures
description: Whether its a fancy dress party or a dash out the door to catch the school bus, OshKosh B’gosh has the trendiest kids shoes that fit perfectly for every stage of growing up. From sparkle shoes for girls to toddler sandals and boys sneakers, we have styles for every activity and season. Durable and comfy, we’ve got all the coolest styles, from gladiators and buckle sandals to bow shoes, jellies, and pom-pom espadrilles. Whether you are looking for baby sandals, toddler shoes, or shoes for kids, we have got them all!
